p.text: Necessity for a competent platform to connect people, organizations requiring help with enthusiastic volunteers.
OlaAmigos connects people based on common grounds, not restricted to differently abled needs or specific NGOs.
Provide for the full functionality of any operating system's accessibility features
Doesn't override with user defined Settings and color contrasts
Ola Amigos! The one-stop solution that liaisons the NGOs, volunteers and provides a comprehensive podium for all activities from there on…
Finds a match when a request is created
When no matches are found, the system notifies the requestor automatically when one becomes available
- Volunteer who can provide the aid
- Further priority based on the connection history & volunteer rating
Admin can authenticate, warn or blacklist a Volunteer.
Volunteer will be considered for match only if he is authentic.
Contact numbers of willing users are only shared, otherwise communication is through emails
Admin validates the information provided by any User
- Price $28.80, infrastructure setup available. Application deployment to be done
- Price $5, the entire setup from software installation and application deployment to be done
Scalable for moving to the next band with both hosting options at a higher price
Wide range of plugins which enabled us to build the app faster end to end
Analytics charts with easy meteor integration
JAWS - Job Access With Speech is the world's most popular screen reader. Ola Amigos is compatible with JAWS.
Application is operational with keyboard actions to assist differently abled
Code has been run through JsHint, the latest de-facto Java script Code Quality Analyser
Complies to the JsHint standards (with minor issues)
